羅莎琳·薩斯曼·耶洛曾獲得[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[傅爾布萊特計畫|傅爾布萊特獎學金]]<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://massivesci.com/articles/science-hero-rosalyn-sussman-yalow-facts-insulin-diabetes-blood-radioimmunoassay/ |title=Meet Nobel Prize winner Rosalyn Sussman Yalow, who let doctors see into your blood |last=Harrod |first=Jordan |website=Massive Science |date=2019-05-12 |access-date=2019-07-22 |archive-date=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716125126/https://massivesci.com/articles/science-hero-rosalyn-sussman-yalow-facts-insulin-diabetes-blood-radioimmunoassay/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，這是一項[[美國政府|美國政府]]資助的國際教育交流計劃，該計劃主要以提供優秀獎學金，為該領域提供競爭性，同時贊助參與者在自有領域進行國際交流，這些領域包括科學、商業、學術、公共服務、政府部門、藝術等等。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://us.fulbrightonline.org/about |title=Overview & History |website=Fulbright U.S. Student Program |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329174957/https://us.fulbrightonline.org/about |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1961年，耶洛獲得{{le|美國糖尿病協會|American Diabetes Association}}頒發的禮來獎<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.nobelprize.org/womenwhochangedscience/stories/rosalyn-yalow |title=Meet Nobel Prize winner Rosalyn Sussman Yalow, who let doctors see into your blood |website=Women who changed science |access-date=2019-07-22 |archive-date=2021-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322094514/https://www.nobelprize.org/womenwhochangedscience/stories/rosalyn-yalow |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該協會是世界上最大的糖尿病及其併發症醫學協會，該協會為多達100名學者提供獎學金，並舉辦科學會議進行交流。此外，協會還為這些學者提供教育和培訓課程，使其成為專業教育計劃教師，並且可臨床管理相關疾病。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.diabetes.org/newsroom/press-releases/2014/scholars-awards.html |title=American Diabetes Association, Lilly Announce New Scholars Program for 74th Annual Scientific Sessions |website=American Diabetes Association |date=2014-01-24 |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329183750/http://www.diabetes.org/newsroom/press-releases/2014/scholars-awards.html |archive-date=2019-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

1971年時，耶洛獲頒[[蓋爾德納國際獎|蓋爾德納基金會國際獎]]<ref name="Awards">{{cite book | language = en |last=King-Thom |first=Chung |date= |title=Women Pioneers of Medical Research: Biographies of 25 Outstanding Scientists |publisher=McFarland |year=2014 |page=175 |isbn=9780786458172 }}</ref>{{rp|175}}，該獎項旨在表彰世界上最具創造力及成就的生物醫學家，感謝他們推動人類的發展。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://gairdner.org/about/about-gairdner/ |title=About Gairdner |website=Gairdner Foundation |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225100219/https://gairdner.org/about/about-gairdner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年，耶洛獲頒{{le|美國醫師學會|American College of Physicians|美國醫師學會獎}}<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://cwp.library.ucla.edu/Phase2/Yalow,_Rosalyn_Sussman@861234567.html |title=Rosalyn Sussman Yalow |website=CWP at UCLA |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211223929/http://cwp.library.ucla.edu/Phase2/Yalow,_Rosalyn_Sussman@861234567.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該獎項旨在表彰獲獎者在內科學的傑出貢獻。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.acponline.org/about-acp/awards-masterships-and-competitions |title=Awards, Masterships and Competitions |website=American College of Physicians |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329175011/https://www.acponline.org/about-acp/awards-masterships-and-competitions |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1972年，耶洛因卓越研究而被授予{{le|威廉·尚寧·密頓|William Shainline Middleton|威廉·尚寧·密頓獎}}<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.beyondcurie.com/rosalyn-sussman-yalow |title=Rosalyn Sussman Yalow - The woman behind the radioimmunoassay |website=Beyond Curie |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106074844/https://www.beyondcurie.com/rosalyn-sussman-yalow |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該獎項是每年生物醫學實驗研究和開發服務最高榮譽，授予資深生物醫學研究家，以表彰他們傑出的科學貢獻和成就，以及改善退伍軍人的醫療保健。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.research.va.gov/services/blrd/research-awards.cfm |title=Office of Research & Development |website=U.S. Department of Veterans Affairs |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329174957/https://www.research.va.gov/services/blrd/research-awards.cfm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|language=en|url=http://permanent.access.gpo.gov/gpo37496/ORD-85yrHistory.pdf|title=A historical look at the establishment of the Department of Veterans Affairs Research & Development Program|last=Hays|first=Marguerite Hays|date=2010|website=U.S. Government Publishing Office|publisher=Department of Veterans Affairs Research & Development Program|access-date=2016-10-02|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516103717/https://permanent.access.gpo.gov/gpo37496/ORD-85yrHistory.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，耶洛還獲得{{le|內分泌學會|Endocrine Society}}科赫獎<ref name="Awards"/>{{rp|175}}，該獎項授予獲獎者在內分泌領域的卓越研究、教育和臨床實驗等。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.endocrine.org/awards#!?sort=_contentstartdate |title=Awards |website=Endocrine Society |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329195034/https://www.endocrine.org/awards#!?sort=_contentstartdate |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1975年，耶洛和{{le|所羅門·柏森|Solomon Berson|柏森}}共同获得{{link-en|AMA科学成就奖|AMA Scientific Achievement Award}}，以表彰兩人在科學成就方面的傑出貢獻。<ref>{{Cite web |language=en |url=https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-rosalyn-yalow-american-medical-physicist-135089005.html |title=Rosalyn Yalow, American Medical Physicist |website=alamy |access-date=2018-05-16 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106074908/https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-rosalyn-yalow-american-medical-physicist-135089005.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>隔年，耶洛成为第一位获得[[拉斯克基礎醫學研究獎|拉斯克基礎醫學研究獎]]的女性得主<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=Albert Lasker Basic Medical Research Award|url=http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/1976_b_description.htm|publisher=Lasker Foundation|access-date=2018-05-14|archive-date=2015-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918232648/http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards/1976_b_description.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該獎項由{{le|阿爾伯特·拉斯克|Albert Lasker}}和{{le|瑪麗·沃德·拉斯克|Mary Lasker}}於1945年創立，旨在表彰醫學領域作出突出貢獻的科學家、醫生和公共服務人員。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=The Lasker Awards |url=http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards-overview/ |website=Albert and Mary Lasker Foundation |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329174957/http://www.laskerfoundation.org/awards-overview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1977年，耶洛与[[罗歇·吉耶曼|罗歇·吉耶曼]]和[[安德鲁·沙利|安德鲁·沙利]]共同获得[[诺贝尔生理学或医学奖|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖]]，她是歷屆第六位女性及第一位美國籍女性在科學領域獲得諾貝爾獎，同時也是繼[[格蒂·科里|格蒂·科里]]之后，第二位获得[[诺贝尔生理学或医学奖|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖]]的美国女性。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.mediatheque.lindau-nobel.org/research-profile/laureate-yalow |title=Research Profile: Rosalyn Yalow |last=Bonolis |first=Luisa |website=Foundation Lindau Nobel Laureate Meetings |date=2019-05-12 |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831104323/https://www.mediatheque.lindau-nobel.org/research-profile/laureate-yalow |dead-url=no }}</ref>获奖理由是研发[[肽类激素|肽类激素]]的[[放射免疫分析|放射免疫分析]]技术，這是一种在无须采用生物测定方法的情况下用于检测[[抗原|抗原]]（例如，[[血清|血清]]之中病毒、[[激素|激素]]、藥物等水平）的实验室测定方法。通過測量人體內的物質，可以對肝炎等疾病進行血液篩查。此外，该技术也可用于测量抗生素的有效性和药物的剂量水平。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/Rosalyn-Yalow |title=Rosalyn S. Yalow - American medical physicist |date=2019-07-15 |publisher=Britannica.com |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archive-date=2021-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503102424/https://www.britannica.com/biography/Rosalyn-Yalow |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1978年，耶洛獲選為[[美国文理科学院|美国文理科学院]]院士<ref name="Awards"/>{{rp|175}}<ref name="Straus222">{{Citation|language = en |last=Straus|first=Eugene|title=Rosalyn Yalow: Nobel Laureate: Her Life and Work in Medicine |year=2000|publisher=Basic Books|isbn=978-0-7382-0263-1|pages=222–223|bibcode=1999MedPh..26..663S|doi=10.1118/1.598828}}</ref>，該職位為職涯初期學者科研人士提供科學或工程方面的培訓訓練，並讓其了解與科研相關的公共政策和行政方面訊息。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Fellowships |url=https://www.amacad.org/about/fellowships |website=American Academy of Arts & Sciences |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2021-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505081738/https://www.amacad.org/about/fellowships |dead-url=no }}</ref>1986年，耶洛獲頒[[紐約科學院|紐約科學院]]{{le|亞伯拉罕·克雷西·莫里遜|Abraham Cressy Morrison|亞伯拉罕·克雷西·莫里遜自然科學獎}}，該獎項旨在頒發給紐約科學院內最佳科學論文創作者。<ref>{{cite journal |year=1944 |editor1-last=Waldo |editor1-first=Miner Roy |title= The New York Academy of Sciences announces the A. Cressy Morrison prize contest for 1946  |url= https://archive.org/stream/in.ernet.dli.2015.21502/2015.21502.Transactions-Of-The-New-York-Academy-Of-Sciences-Vol-7-1944#page/n3/mode/2up |access-date=2018-05-14 |format= PDF |journal= Transactions Of The New York Academy of Sciences |series= 2 |language= en |publisher=New York Academy of Sciences |volume= 7 |issue= |pages= 168-169 |isbn=978-1347923184 }}</ref>1988年，耶洛获得[[美国国家科学奖章|美国国家科学奖章]]<ref name="Awards"/>{{rp|176}}，該獎章為美國科學及技術領域內的最高榮譽獎章。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Celebrating America's Highest Honor for Science and Technology |url=https://www.nationalmedals.org/about |website=National Science & Technology Medals Foundation |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329174958/https://www.nationalmedals.org/about |dead-url=no }}</ref>1993年，耶洛入選為[[美國國家女性名人堂|美國國家女性名人堂]]。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Rosalyn S. Yalow |url=https://www.womenofthehall.org/inductee/rosalyn-s-yalow/ |website=National Women's Hall of Fame |access-date=2018-05-14 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329174956/https://www.womenofthehall.org/inductee/rosalyn-s-yalow/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

